				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Greetings from Louisiana!
<br />

<br />
Thanks for the Gaming Forum--here's hoping it doesn't degenerate into anything bad very fast.
<br />

<br />
The business model for computer games seems to be evolving, and Massively Multiplayer On-Line Role-Playing Games (MMORPG's) seem to be leading the charge.
<br />

<br />
I've played Everquest, Ultima OnLine, and Dark Age of Camelot, but none to the high levels.
<br />

<br />
'IF' you could design a better mousetrap, what practical improvements would you personally like to see implemented?
<br />

<br />
Interested in your opinions.....
<br />

<br />
Doc</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
